A very WIP minecraft mod I'm making for a different (better hopefully) Hypixel Skyblock experience with various tweaks (mainly just more playable ping as it'll be single player).
I expect a playable base will be completed by the end of 2026 but obviously life can be quite unpredictable.

Big thanks to: the entire Hypixel Skyblock team for making it in the first place, the developers of NEU, SBA and Skyblocker which I've taken much inspiration from and the Neoforge team.